## Fourth day

### Stockach to Memminger h√ºtte

We are finally back to the E5 track.

After our breakfast, the owner of our guest house said there was a bus that goes from Bach to the start of a trail to the h√ºtte. And most importantly, they will ride us to that bus stop. The bus picked us up at 8:30 AM. The track up to the h√ºtte is beautiful. Most of the way, it rained, so we were wet. When we almost reached the h√ºtte, we saw wild goats. They were so close that it seemed like you could touch them.

